{"tid":1476591,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"818 遊行！！！一定要帶裝！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-16T00:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T07:37:32.000Z","uid":51064,"like":23,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"96c4edb7183695e340a06bd82d15ac3010c02684","tid":1476591,"uid":51064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:50:05.000Z","msg":"你地班人叫人唔帶裝係咪想謀殺！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班犬反對左遊行架，你就算和平都唔保證佢會唔會反癲扔你！ 你地係咪想連累啲手足！<br />\n<br />\n係咁話要和班非進行，唔佔路乜春都唔做？你地係咪唔記得左佔路係和理非最低消費？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地最多唔死守路，只係行！跟原本路線行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最多行完保證唔守路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：黑心講句 我最想佢扔催淚彈，等班和理非都食埋就知催淚彈不可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />然後慢慢加入勇武既行列<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一句講曬：818 帶裝！"},{"pid":"8edb6db12e56c8de134ca6d0c455947c3a31ae74","tid":1476591,"uid":79046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:52:05.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行過路過入嚟望下，千載難逢嘅大好機會！！十八區we connect，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">823人鏈823人鏈823人鏈</span></span></strong>，百萬人齊築香江路！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［和理非升級］一生人一次嘅機會嚟喇！！！！想唔想上Buzzfeed 9GAG？！？！？！？！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https: